	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				每一个房间都只有一种颜色，但光线和转折的墙面让每个房间都非常独特。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>
	<span>越来越多的幼儿园融入了设计者对于早期教育的想法。有的放任玩耍，寓教于乐，也有通过建筑设计来影响儿童的世界观。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>这家幼儿园在韩国首尔，外观上最明显的标志是不规则的屋顶，虽然还是用的青瓦，它的起伏和转折并不连贯，倒像是将不同幢房子拼在一起了。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/a64342a75ab7.jpg" width="1080" height="487" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/12462d9d0bbc.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/e80fa1219d2e.jpg" width="1080" height="715" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/4642d6826644.jpg" width="1080" height="702" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>如果有机会俯瞰屋顶则会发现，每一块小的坡面屋顶都开了一个小的天窗，它对应着二楼不同的独立房间。设计者的初衷是建立“house within a house”，他们认为幼儿园的建筑能带给儿童最初对城市的感知，幼儿园里的中庭、走廊和房间分别代表城市里的广场、街道和建筑。从这个角度来看，每一个房间都是公寓的延伸，也应该是家庭舒适感的延伸。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/a00bea7427c9.jpg" width="1080" height="1296" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>幼儿园有一个很大的中庭，充当城市里广场的职能，连接了一楼和二楼以及各个房间。它可以作为儿童室内活动的场地和办活动的地方，儿童在这里的活动也是在监督之下的，很有安全感。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/8733e018e78a.jpg" width="1080" height="723" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/eb61000f23af.jpg" width="1080" height="918" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/11c87200fedc.jpg" width="1080" height="756" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/2109f60237ee.jpg" width="1080" height="709" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/188813b316b0.jpg" width="661" height="1000" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>二楼室内里也能感受到不规则的屋顶，每个房间刷成了不同的颜色，有一种活泼和纯净。这种故意保留下来的错位是设计者想要做出的折纸感。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span><span>光线从最上面的天窗照射进来，周围零星点缀了方形的小灯，有点教堂的感觉。</span>室内室外两种灯光配合着建筑墙面的转折，让房间的颜色有了深浅变化，很丰富。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span><span>此外，房间里打开了高高低低的窗户，低矮的窗户是为儿童设计的，以便让他们能看到外面的自然。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/4c6913fa4276.jpg" width="1062" height="1000" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/54ddfa87cfcb.jpg" width="1080" height="723" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/302d4ec888f0.jpg" width="1080" height="714" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/0148c96cb2a7.jpg" width="1044" height="1000" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/35668f0f279a.jpg" width="1080" height="721" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/1342d7e50d45.jpg" width="1080" height="723" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/bf9dc62cbbeb.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>这家幼儿园位于德寿宫附近，将招收 0 到 5 岁的儿童。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/2d7793237ec8.jpg" width="1080" height="823" title="进门处" alt="进门处" /><span>进门处</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/fbf940bed4b0.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title="洗手池" alt="洗手池" /><span>洗手池</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/28462bba5b19.jpg" width="1080" height="737" title="室外" alt="室外" /><span>室外</span> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/f6c72140d97b.jpg" width="909" height="1000" title="一楼平面图" alt="一楼平面图" /><span>一楼平面图</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201601/b1d79e20d299.jpg" width="872" height="1000" title="二楼平面图" alt="二楼平面图" /><span>二楼平面图</span> 
</p>
<p>
	图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.archdaily.com/780339/hangdong-kindergarten-janghwan-cheon-plus-studio-i" target="_blank">archdaily</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
		</div>
	</div>
